{"tid":1783376,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[勞工法例] 工傷補償一問","createTime":"2019-12-14T17:40:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T19:20:41.000Z","uid":96460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"224cd5ce88dd99ff1ba7dfece7bdb6dec31fccb3","tid":1783376,"uid":96460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T17:40:33.000Z","msg":"小妹今年工傷報咗上勞工處<br />\n喺工傷期間舊公司有出底薪，有比醫藥費<br />\n工傷返唔到工都有成2個月<br />\n之後quit埋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最近收到「補償評估證明書」（即表格5）<br />\n但21日到啦 都未收到任何補償 <br />\n咁我可以點？</span><br />\n<br />\nFYI<br />\n勞工處話「在其他情況下，勞工處僱員補償科會給僱主及僱員簽發一份列明補償款額的「補償評估證明書」（即表格5），僱主必須在證明書發出後21 天內將補償款項或未付的餘額全數支付給僱員。」"},{"pid":"7f46f95ae2ff4fdef39c569a2d4483ffb211ede1","tid":1783376,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T17:51:27.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bf6ebb00dbc713e16d8727acd59eb86d8f1ef699","tid":1783376,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T19:20:23.000Z","msg":"同勞工處投訴，你有權索取附加費<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OUsA0gn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOUsA0gn.png&h=fa293254&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48c48a95b1c6efe822f5f10498b3aaade38c0841","tid":1783376,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T19:20:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">聽日下午三點要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n愛丁堡有社福集會！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J1TAfH2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ1TAfH2.jpg&h=4a3f8b6c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}